{"name":"Accurate Attack","type":"talent","img":"systems/mutants-and-masterminds-3e/assets/icons/talent.svg","system":{"description":"<p>When you make an accurate attack, you can take a penalty of up to –5 on the effect modifier of the attack and add the same number (up to +5) to your attack bonus.</p>","equipement":false,"rang":1,"edit":true,"listEffectsVariantes":{}},"effects":[],"_id":"2hsbvk3ljj"}
{"name":"Agile Feint","type":"talent","img":"systems/mutants-and-masterminds-3e/assets/icons/talent.svg","system":{"description":"<p>You can use your Acrobatics bonus or movement speed rank in place of Deception to feint and trick in combat.</p>","equipement":false,"rang":1,"edit":true,"listEffectsVariantes":{}},"effects":[],"_id":"lnjpuj3ympn"}
{"name":"All-out Attack","type":"talent","img":"systems/mutants-and-masterminds-3e/assets/icons/talent.svg","system":{"description":"<p>When you make an all-out attack, you can take a penalty of up to –5 on your active defenses (Dodge and Parry) and add the same number (up to +5) to your attack bonus.</p>","equipement":false,"rang":1,"edit":true,"listEffectsVariantes":{}},"effects":[],"_id":"jeif1a4kqk"}
{"name":"Animal Empathy","type":"talent","img":"systems/mutants-and-masterminds-3e/assets/icons/talent.svg","system":{"description":"<p>You have a special connection with animals. You can use interaction skills on animals normally, and do not have to speak a language the animal understands.</p>","equipement":false,"rang":1,"edit":true,"listEffectsVariantes":{}},"effects":[],"_id":"muh4rxfgoz"}
{"name":"Artificer","type":"talent","img":"systems/mutants-and-masterminds-3e/assets/icons/talent.svg","system":{"description":"<p>You can use the Expertise: Magic skill to create temporary magical devices.</p>","equipement":false,"rang":1,"edit":true,"listEffectsVariantes":{}},"effects":[],"_id":"ut3o6z8exza"}
{"name":"Assessment","type":"talent","img":"systems/mutants-and-masterminds-3e/assets/icons/talent.svg","system":{"description":"<p>You can use Insight to able to judge an opponent’s relative combat capabilities.</p>","equipement":false,"rang":1,"edit":true,"listEffectsVariantes":{}},"effects":[],"_id":"qvgtj22m27n"}
{"name":"Attractive","type":"talent","img":"systems/mutants-and-masterminds-3e/assets/icons/talent.svg","system":{"description":"<p>You are particularly attractive, giving you a +2 circumstance bonus on Deception and Persuasion checks to deceive, mislead, or influence others who are attracted to you. Rank 2 gives a +5 bonus.</p>","equipement":false,"rang":1,"edit":true,"listEffectsVariantes":{}},"effects":[],"_id":"1u6imcksunn"}
{"name":"Beginner's Luck","type":"talent","img":"systems/mutants-and-masterminds-3e/assets/icons/talent.svg","system":{"description":"<p>By spending a hero point, you gain an effective 5 ranks in a skill in which you currently have 0 ranks.</p>","equipement":false,"rang":1,"edit":true,"listEffectsVariantes":{}},"effects":[],"_id":"1x3ydazep1u"}
{"name":"Benefit","type":"talent","img":"systems/mutants-and-masterminds-3e/assets/icons/talent.svg","system":{"description":"<p>You have some significant social or structural benefit, such as wealth, status, or a secret identity. Each rank provides one benefit.</p>","equipement":false,"rang":1,"edit":true,"listEffectsVariantes":{}},"effects":[],"_id":"gl9gxepsbi"}
{"name":"Chokehold","type":"talent","img":"systems/mutants-and-masterminds-3e/assets/icons/talent.svg","system":{"description":"<p>If you successfully grab and maintain a hold on an opponent, you can suffocate them.</p>","equipement":false,"rang":1,"edit":true,"listEffectsVariantes":{}},"effects":[],"_id":"0g33t60tyzk8"}
{"name":"Connected","type":"talent","img":"systems/mutants-and-masterminds-3e/assets/icons/talent.svg","system":{"description":"<p>You know people who can help you out. You can call in favors by making a Persuasion check.</p>","equipement":false,"rang":1,"edit":true,"listEffectsVariantes":{}},"effects":[],"_id":"4sler3n6rbm"}
{"name":"Contacts","type":"talent","img":"systems/mutants-and-masterminds-3e/assets/icons/talent.svg","system":{"description":"<p>You have extensive contacts. You can make an Investigation check to gather information in only one minute.</p>","equipement":false,"rang":1,"edit":true,"listEffectsVariantes":{}},"effects":[],"_id":"df7o83mrli9"}
{"name":"Daze","type":"talent","img":"systems/mutants-and-masterminds-3e/assets/icons/talent.svg","system":{"description":"<p>You can make a Deception or Intimidation check as a standard action to cause an opponent to hesitate in combat.</p>","equipement":false,"rang":2,"edit":true,"listEffectsVariantes":{}},"effects":[],"_id":"zx4jhgl104o"}
{"name":"Defensive Attack","type":"talent","img":"systems/mutants-and-masterminds-3e/assets/icons/talent.svg","system":{"description":"<p>Trade up to -5 attack bonus for an equal bonus (+5) to active defenses.</p>","equipement":false,"rang":1,"edit":true,"listEffectsVariantes":{}},"effects":[],"_id":"rdtqzry5fdd"}
{"name":"Defensive Roll","type":"talent","img":"systems/mutants-and-masterminds-3e/assets/icons/talent.svg","system":{"description":"<p>Receive a bonus to Toughness equal to rank. This is an active defense and is lost if vulnerable or defenseless.</p>","equipement":false,"rang":1,"edit":true,"listEffectsVariantes":{}},"effects":[],"_id":"y73ri2u6afk"}
